# Stuga Home Assistant Dashboard
# ================================
#
# Configuration is done through the in-app setup wizard.
# These environment variables are optional and only needed for
# server-side API proxy functionality (if used).
#
# The dashboard primarily uses WebSocket connection configured in-app,
# with credentials stored securely in browser localStorage.

# Server-side (optional - for API proxy)
# HOME_ASSISTANT_URL=http://homeassistant.local:8123
# HOME_ASSISTANT_TOKEN=your_long_lived_access_token

# Note: No NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are needed.
# Client-side configuration is done through the in-app setup flow.
